      <li>üßä Cooler Master MasterLiquid V2</li>
      <li>üõ† MSI B760 Gaming Plus WiFi Motherboard</li>
      <li>‚ö° 700W be quiet! 80+ Gold PSU</li>
      <li>üíæ 1TB Samsung 980 Pro NVMe SSD</li>
      <li>üì° PCIe Wi-Fi Card</li>
      <li>üñ•Ô∏è Case: Kolink Observatory Lite Mesh (White)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="benchmarks">
